# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WHAT IS INTENTIONALLY *NOT* IGNORED
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# .mcp.json                 ← MCP server config (no secrets, committed via !.mcp.json above)
# specs/                    ← feature spec artifacts (committed via !specs/ above)
# services/profiles.yaml    ← profile composition definitions (committed)
# services/**/service.yaml  ← per-service metadata + codename (committed)
# go.sum                    ← dependency lock file (must be committed)
# **/testdata/              ← test fixtures (committed)
#
# ─── TO SHARE .claude/ OR .specify/ WITH THE TEAM ──────────
# Option A: Remove the ignore lines above (un-ignore everything)
# Option B: Copy to a shared dotfiles/tooling repo
# Option C: Add individual !.claude/agents/*.md exceptions here
